This is a Vanilla TypeScript + Vite project with Tailwind CSS.

STYLING RULES:
- Use Tailwind CSS utility classes for ALL styling
- Apply classes via JavaScript/TypeScript DOM manipulation or in index.html
- Do NOT create custom CSS files — use Tailwind classes

IMPORTANT:
- Always run `npm install && npm run dev` to start
- Use TypeScript for all new files (.ts)
- Never use `vite` directly — always use `npm run dev`
